      <title>金正恩妹妹警告韩国将为散发传单付出“惨痛代价”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/kim-jong-un-s-sister-warns-south-korea-it-will-pay-gruesome-price-for-leaflets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜领导人金正恩的妹妹警告首尔，越过边境散发反平壤传单将让其付出“惨痛”的代价，这表明朝鲜在向韩国发放装满垃圾的气球后可能会加大赌注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/kim-jong-un-s-sister-warns-south-korea-it-will-pay-gruesome-price-for-leaflets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 03:07:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普副总统候选人万斯称中国是美国“最大威胁”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/trump-s-vp-pick-vance-says-china-is-the-biggest-threat-to-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自被任命为唐纳德·特朗普的竞选搭档以来，JD 万斯在首次接受采访时将中国称为美国面临的最大威胁，并强调一旦当选，美国政府可能会对北京采取强硬立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/trump-s-vp-pick-vance-says-china-is-the-biggest-threat-to-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 03:06:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>情报机构证实朝鲜驻古巴外交官 11 月叛逃韩国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-16/urgent-north-korean-diplomat-in-cuba-defected-to-south-korea-in-november-seoul-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔，韩国（美联社）——韩国情报机构周二称，一名驻古巴的朝鲜外交官已逃往韩国，这是近年来朝鲜统治精英成员一系列叛逃事件中的最新一起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-16/urgent-north-korean-diplomat-in-cuba-defected-to-south-korea-in-november-seoul-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 02:22:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银称美国 60% 关税将使中国经济增长率减半</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/us-tariffs-at-60-would-halve-china-s-growth-rate-ubs-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团最新研究显示，如果对中国输美的所有出口产品征收 60% 的新关税，中国的年经济增长率将减少一半以上，这凸显出前总统唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫后北京面临的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/us-tariffs-at-60-would-halve-china-s-growth-rate-ubs-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 02:17:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普枪击事件后耳朵缠着绷带出席共和党全国委员会盛大开幕式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/rnc-2024-trump-vance-allies-attack-biden-s-handling-of-us-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在遭遇暗杀后首次公开露面，一条白色绷带遮住了他的右耳，共和党人聚集在一起，第三次提名他为总统候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/rnc-2024-trump-vance-allies-attack-biden-s-handling-of-us-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 01:48:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普选择万斯加剧与共和党外交政策保守派的分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/vance-s-foreign-policy-views-widen-trump-s-break-with-republican-old-guard</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普选择 JD 万斯作为竞选伙伴，标志着他与共和党外交政策老派的彻底决裂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/vance-s-foreign-policy-views-widen-trump-s-break-with-republican-old-guard</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊隆·马斯克每月向亲特朗普超级政治行动委员会捐赠 4500 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/pro-trump-super-pac-backed-by-elon-musk-raises-8-8-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克承诺每月向支持唐纳德·特朗普的政治团体投入 4500 万美元，此举将为共和党候选人在 11 月大选前的连任竞选提供大量资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/pro-trump-super-pac-backed-by-elon-musk-raises-8-8-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 23:48:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>从埃隆·马斯克到大卫·萨克斯，硅谷的特朗普支持者欢呼万斯成为副总统人选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/why-jd-vance-as-trump-s-vp-pick-has-silicon-valley-celebrating</link>
      <description><![CDATA[硅谷的主要投资者对唐纳德·特朗普选择俄亥俄州参议员、前风险投资家 JD Vance 作为竞选搭档表示欢迎，如果这位前总统 11 月入主白宫，此举将使科技行业更接近华盛顿的中心舞台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/why-jd-vance-as-trump-s-vp-pick-has-silicon-valley-celebrating</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 23:33:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国特勤局局长称特朗普枪击事件“不可接受”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/us-secret-service-chief-calls-trump-shooting-unacceptable-lynn50d6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国特勤局局长在前总统唐纳德·特朗普遭暗杀未遂后面临严厉的公众审查和调查，他表示枪击事件“根本不应该发生”，并发誓要“立即做出改变”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/us-secret-service-chief-calls-trump-shooting-unacceptable-lynn50d6</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 23:10:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称特勤局是否在枪击事件中犯错“尚无定论”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/secret-service-beefing-up-biden-trump-protection-post-shooting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示他感到安全，但有人质疑美国特勤局是否应该采取更多措施来预防针对唐纳德·特朗普的暗杀企图。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/secret-service-beefing-up-biden-trump-protection-post-shooting</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:27:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
